16:59.954 --> 17:02.666
I did, and now I don't.

17:02.922 --> 17:05.189
So get out of the car.

17:06.335 --> 17:08.136
[ Seat belt unbuckles ]

17:10.765 --> 17:13.019
[ Engine starts,
truck door closes ]

17:21.135 --> 17:22.579
10 Grand each from Monica.

17:22.648 --> 17:24.493
It's an advance
on the credit cards.

17:24.704 --> 17:26.782
She thinks we're gonna get
north of 100k.

17:26.858 --> 17:28.345
Holy shit.

17:28.423 --> 17:29.837
And the checks?

17:29.972 --> 17:31.197
She's got a guy to kite 'em,

17:31.222 --> 17:32.627
but she's never worked
with him before,

17:32.651 --> 17:34.650
I say we eat 'em,
not risk it.

17:34.761 --> 17:37.534
Well, it's a 100 in cards,
196 in cash.

17:37.596 --> 17:39.627
- That'll be fine.
- Yeah.

17:39.842 --> 17:42.158
You got a shredder?

17:43.252 --> 17:45.072
- No.
- No?

17:45.352 --> 17:46.861
Spark up the fire pit.

17:46.963 --> 17:49.501
- No.
- What? What are you worried about?

17:49.548 --> 17:51.384
We'll get rid of the ashes
when we're done.

17:51.486 --> 17:53.553
It's not up to code.
Oh, Jesus Christ.

17:53.633 --> 17:56.377
It's a real thing, okay? I can't
afford to get cited right now.

17:56.455 --> 17:58.017
I'll take care of it.

17:58.152 --> 18:00.658
Don't sit on 'em. Do it asap.

18:00.922 --> 18:02.355
I know how to burn shit.

18:02.459 --> 18:04.376
[ Cellphone vibrating ]

18:06.040 --> 18:09.079
- Is it J?
- Yeah, he ain't showin'.

18:09.131 --> 18:10.540
He still nursing that leg?

18:10.601 --> 18:13.101
Well, I saw him this morning with smurf.
He looked fine to me.

18:13.136 --> 18:15.837
She's probably giving him shit
for doing a job with us.

18:16.042 --> 18:17.696
<i>♪♪</i>

18:17.844 --> 18:19.641
And the swamp thing returns.

18:19.774 --> 18:21.373
What the hell happened to you?

18:21.719 --> 18:23.368
Okay if I grab some food?

18:23.480 --> 18:24.977
Get any of my texts?

18:25.063 --> 18:26.868
I'm hungry, bro. Can I...

18:27.024 --> 18:30.530
[ Scoffs ] Yeah, go ahead.
Knock yourself out.

18:30.868 --> 18:33.969
<i>♪♪</i>

18:34.026 --> 18:36.860
Uh, okay, so, uh...

18:37.196 --> 18:38.762
When can we start divvying up
this cash?

18:38.787 --> 18:40.368
I got bills to pay.

18:40.521 --> 18:42.219
Well, we gotta
launder it first.

18:42.354 --> 18:45.589
He's gonna do 20 at pechanga.
I'm gonna do the same at pala.

18:45.771 --> 18:48.751
That still leaves
a big chunk here.

18:49.338 --> 18:51.273
[ Pope clears throat ]

18:51.907 --> 18:53.160
No.

18:53.318 --> 18:55.047
5 Grand a week.
Who's gonna notice?

18:55.114 --> 18:56.891
And more if business picks up.

18:56.945 --> 18:58.752
(Deran:) No, the feds live
for this shit. Okay?

18:58.776 --> 19:00.493
They love taking down
new businesses. No?

19:00.547 --> 19:02.838
(Baz:) Smurf's been doing it for years.
You want me to be smurf?

19:02.862 --> 19:05.844
If it means we get to spend
the money we steal, yeah.

19:05.869 --> 19:07.626
No! That's not why
I bought this bar, guys.

19:07.688 --> 19:09.002
Then why'd you buy it?
Why'd you buy the bar?

19:09.026 --> 19:11.226
Some of us helped you
buy the bar, by the way.

19:11.463 --> 19:13.459
Okay, you want the cash? Here, take it.
No, I don't want the cash.

19:13.483 --> 19:15.533
Don't be an idiot. Deran, listen.
Deran, listen, to me.

19:15.557 --> 19:17.012
- We need to move the money now.
- No! No!

19:17.036 --> 19:19.485
We're not going through
my bar.

19:19.906 --> 19:21.602
Okay?

19:22.141 --> 19:23.607
[ Sighs ]

19:41.413 --> 19:45.085
Don't get hot and do
anything stupid with that thing.

19:45.661 --> 19:47.794
I won't if they won't.

19:50.309 --> 19:52.109
Ahh.

19:52.640 --> 19:55.843
What's taking your boys
so long?

19:56.406 --> 19:58.296
My boys aren't coming.

19:58.510 --> 20:01.478
This is our problem,
not theirs.

20:02.573 --> 20:04.757
It's just us?

20:05.628 --> 20:06.937
Yep.

20:07.202 --> 20:08.545
Just us.

20:08.570 --> 20:12.105
We're meeting Javi
by the jetty in one hour.

20:12.746 --> 20:15.180
Kind of like
the old days, huh?

20:17.888 --> 20:19.640
Remember?

20:19.978 --> 20:22.845
[ Chuckles ] The shit we did
when we were young.

20:24.933 --> 20:27.034
'Cause we had to.

20:28.148 --> 20:30.440
We didn't have a choice.

20:30.734 --> 20:31.875
[ Clicks ]

20:32.054 --> 20:34.578
Javi just got screwed.

20:37.982 --> 20:39.906
We owe that kid this money.

20:40.011 --> 20:41.543
[ Gun cocks ]

20:46.824 --> 20:48.664
I'm sorry, smurf.

20:48.894 --> 20:52.734
♪♪

20:55.521 --> 20:57.622
Let's go.

21:01.227 --> 21:03.117
I am sorry.

21:04.554 --> 21:06.222
You know for years,

21:06.310 --> 21:09.250
you paid Manny off to keep
his mouth shut.

21:09.656 --> 21:13.351
- But me?
- You're Craig's father, for God sake.

21:13.502 --> 21:15.218
We had a baby together.

21:15.391 --> 21:17.726
Does he know that?! Huh?!

21:17.815 --> 21:19.445
No, he <i> doesn't</i> know that

21:19.515 --> 21:21.085
'cause you never told him!

21:21.141 --> 21:23.542
You treat me like
I'm an employee!

21:29.934 --> 21:31.802
[ Cord clatters ]

21:32.918 --> 21:36.020
♪♪

21:37.008 --> 21:39.609
I don't know where
you think you're goin'.

21:41.418 --> 21:44.487
Anywhere but with you.

21:44.817 --> 21:46.450
Huh?

21:52.053 --> 21:56.500
So you're gonna leave Javi
standing out there on the beach?

21:56.979 --> 21:59.843
- I'll take my chances.
- Good luck.

22:00.276 --> 22:03.773
Not only are you
on the run from Javi,

22:04.390 --> 22:07.148
now you're on the run
from me.

22:10.074 --> 22:13.851
♪♪

22:21.052 --> 22:23.286
[ birds calling ]

22:23.335 --> 22:24.701
[ Man shouts indistinctly ]

22:24.757 --> 22:28.584
♪♪

22:48.612 --> 22:51.980
J, you wanna keep working with
us, you can't miss a meeting.

22:52.084 --> 22:54.269
<i>Yeah, I'm sorry, man.</i>
Where were you?

22:54.448 --> 22:56.573
[ Grunts ] My leg opened up.

22:56.788 --> 22:58.175
<i>Did smurf take you
to a hospital?</i>

22:58.286 --> 23:00.440
No, no, the drugstore
to get more antiseptic.

23:00.522 --> 23:01.775
And that took all morning?
[ Siren whooping ]

23:01.799 --> 23:03.839
<i>Dude, half the staples
fell out.</i>

23:04.263 --> 23:06.386
<i>It hurt like a bitch,
so I had to...</i>

23:06.465 --> 23:07.831
[ line disconnects ]

23:07.966 --> 23:09.550
Baz?

23:09.784 --> 23:11.230
[ Whispers ] Shit.

23:24.715 --> 23:26.516
[ Gears shift,
engine turns off ]

23:26.644 --> 23:29.619
♪♪

23:32.595 --> 23:34.347
There you go, man.

23:34.892 --> 23:36.433
Get out of the car.

23:36.661 --> 23:38.042
On your knees.

23:38.147 --> 23:39.680
Hands on your head.

23:42.233 --> 23:43.839
Your wife...

23:44.503 --> 23:46.620
She had a bank account
with 22 Grand in it.

23:46.767 --> 23:48.331
Did you know that?

23:48.564 --> 23:51.332
Probably not, 'cause if you did,
you would've drained it.

23:51.644 --> 23:54.600
Nobody's seen or heard from her
in 2 1/2 months,

23:54.671 --> 23:55.858
and she didn't spend a dime.

23:55.914 --> 23:57.350
What do you think that means?

23:57.524 --> 23:59.061
Excuse me.
Am I under arrest?

23:59.144 --> 24:01.444
'Cause if so,
I'd like to call my lawyer.

24:04.925 --> 24:08.678
[ Lowered voice ] I <i> will</i>
find out what you did to her.

24:09.152 --> 24:10.694
Understand me?

24:15.333 --> 24:19.053
♪♪

24:35.486 --> 24:36.924
[ grunts ]

24:37.006 --> 24:38.773
[ Sighs ]

24:39.244 --> 24:43.221
♪♪

24:55.973 --> 24:57.853
[ bottles shatters ]

24:58.010 --> 25:01.144
♪♪

25:02.223 --> 25:04.067
[ thud ]

25:18.829 --> 25:20.663
[ Thud ]

25:20.900 --> 25:24.228
♪♪

25:44.989 --> 25:48.489
♪♪ The black keys and RZA's "The
baddest man alive" playing...

25:50.861 --> 25:54.481
♪♪

26:02.206 --> 26:05.854
♪♪

26:10.796 --> 26:12.378
[ object clatters ]

26:12.566 --> 26:15.721
♪ I could take the pitchfork
from the devil ♪

26:15.831 --> 26:19.339
♪ I'm the baddest man alive ♪

26:19.458 --> 26:20.958
[ soap dispenser rattles ]

26:21.373 --> 26:25.253
♪ I take no mess
and I take no jive ♪

26:25.278 --> 26:27.042
♪♪

26:27.193 --> 26:32.924
♪ Sometimes I feel like
I can fly ♪

26:33.105 --> 26:35.174
♪ I'm the baddest man alive ♪

26:35.306 --> 26:36.854
[ inhales ]

26:36.878 --> 26:38.315
♪♪

26:38.344 --> 26:39.885
♪ I'm the baddest man alive ♪

26:39.964 --> 26:42.089
[ speaks indistinctly ]

26:42.114 --> 26:43.870
[ Sniffs, exhales sharply ]

26:44.139 --> 26:46.806
[ Line rings ]

26:46.926 --> 26:50.194
<i>You've reached Janine Cody.
Leave a message.</i>

26:50.219 --> 26:51.245
<i>[ Beep ]</i>

26:51.270 --> 26:52.703
[ Sighs ]

26:52.856 --> 26:54.689
♪♪

26:54.823 --> 26:57.307
Hey. Where's smurf?

26:57.560 --> 26:59.573
- I don't know.
- No Lena either?

26:59.673 --> 27:01.240
Yeah. She's at Baz's.

27:01.664 --> 27:03.307
I just ordered a pizza.

27:03.432 --> 27:05.190
You still wanna help me
with chem later?

27:05.460 --> 27:07.326
Sure.

27:12.580 --> 27:14.714
I'll go get my books.

27:20.915 --> 27:24.663
♪♪

27:30.074 --> 27:31.775
[ receiver clatters ]

27:41.486 --> 27:45.743
[ Line rings ]

27:45.874 --> 27:47.236
<i>Hello?</i>

27:47.879 --> 27:49.556
[ Voice breaks ]
I need you.

27:49.807 --> 27:51.974
So two years experience
in long beach, huh?

27:52.047 --> 27:53.900
- Yeah.
- You feel comfortable with all aspects?

27:53.924 --> 27:56.095
Table service, bar, buffet,
setup, and breakdown?

27:56.288 --> 27:58.142
Definitely.
What's in a mojito, Eric?

27:58.245 --> 28:01.900
Uh, rum, lime juice,
and, uh, sugar?

28:02.156 --> 28:04.056
[ Chuckles ]
And mint and club soda.

28:04.230 --> 28:05.829
- Right.
- You'll be fine.

28:05.894 --> 28:08.064
- You ever get seasick?
- No.

28:08.227 --> 28:10.560
Company policy. Sorry.

28:10.696 --> 28:11.822
Bathroom's down the hall.

28:11.888 --> 28:13.658
Unless there's a problem,
job's yours.

28:14.095 --> 28:15.908
Great.

28:16.815 --> 28:19.282
[ Whispers ] Great. [ Sighs ]

28:21.026 --> 28:22.994
[ Sighs ]

28:26.111 --> 28:27.525
Uh...

28:27.612 --> 28:29.025
[ Cup clatters ]

28:34.744 --> 28:37.658
[ Door creaks closed ]

28:38.190 --> 28:40.330
Hey, uh...

28:40.839 --> 28:42.861
I'm gonna need your piss.

28:43.564 --> 28:45.439
What? No.

28:45.503 --> 28:47.937
Hey, man, don't be a dick.
I'll give you 20 bucks.

28:50.605 --> 28:52.105
[ Zips pants ]
Help, help, help!

28:52.181 --> 28:54.127
Hey, hey, hey, hey.
[ Thud ]

28:54.263 --> 28:57.764
- [ Gasps ] Okay.
- Okay, okay, please.

28:57.946 --> 29:00.353
- Okay?
- Yeah. Yeah.

29:00.542 --> 29:02.158
All right.

29:02.492 --> 29:03.767
Now you see that cup?

29:03.893 --> 29:05.103
Yes.

29:05.241 --> 29:07.158
Off we go.

29:09.197 --> 29:10.530
[ Exhales sharply ]

29:10.603 --> 29:12.236
[ Sniffles ]

29:14.729 --> 29:16.963
I... I, uh,

29:17.103 --> 29:19.345
I-I can't...

29:19.451 --> 29:21.484
With... with that.

29:22.524 --> 29:24.267
Oh. Yeah.

29:24.313 --> 29:25.679
[ Sighs ]
[ Urinating ]

29:26.408 --> 29:28.595
Hey, man. Not now.
We're cleaning. Come on.

29:28.697 --> 29:31.033
- Out. Out we go. Not now.
- [ Grunts ] Wait. What?

29:31.146 --> 29:34.353
[ Continues urinating ]

29:34.470 --> 29:35.970
[ Lid clicks ]

29:38.152 --> 29:41.188
Good man. And...

29:43.560 --> 29:45.094
Okay.

29:49.239 --> 29:50.939
Oh. Hey.

29:51.054 --> 29:52.431
You don't do drugs, do you?

29:52.526 --> 29:55.227
- No.
- Good man.

29:57.951 --> 29:59.519
[ Sighs ]

29:59.983 --> 30:01.750
[ Sliding ]

30:05.208 --> 30:06.567
[ Floorboards clatter ]

30:06.907 --> 30:09.630
♪♪

30:09.918 --> 30:12.752
[ bag rustles ]

30:13.621 --> 30:15.604
[ Sliding ]

30:16.198 --> 30:17.965
[ Sighs ]

30:18.304 --> 30:21.721
♪♪

30:25.521 --> 30:28.957
[ power washer whirring ]

30:29.293 --> 30:31.425
[ Horn blares ]

30:31.544 --> 30:33.245
[ Motor revs ]

30:33.418 --> 30:36.261
[ Motor turns off ] What the
hell happened to your bike?

30:36.784 --> 30:38.534
It's a-a long story.

30:38.854 --> 30:40.675
[ Sighs ]

30:41.461 --> 30:43.360
[ Groans ]

30:43.785 --> 30:45.214
What's that?

30:45.654 --> 30:46.987
The $3,300 I owe you.

30:47.115 --> 30:49.880
No, man. That's... that's cash
for having me crash upstairs.

30:49.958 --> 30:51.458
Just take it.
I'm not taking it.

30:51.528 --> 30:53.495
- Take it, man.
- No!

30:54.971 --> 30:56.505
[ Sighs ]

31:01.364 --> 31:03.052
I lost my mind, man.

31:03.209 --> 31:06.208
- I shouldn't have shown up last night.
- You think?

31:07.067 --> 31:09.685
Could've really
screwed us, man.

31:10.065 --> 31:12.332
Especially for a job
that you shit on

31:12.444 --> 31:13.636
and you didn't even wanna do
in the first place.

31:13.660 --> 31:16.094
Look, I thought you weren't
gonna do it, okay?

31:16.354 --> 31:18.329
Without me, you know, once you
thought I was being serious.

31:18.353 --> 31:19.802
I mean, the others? Fine.
But <i> you?</i>

31:19.843 --> 31:21.224
No. No.

31:21.319 --> 31:23.208
Look, I can't keep
doing this, okay?

31:23.304 --> 31:25.068
I gotta be able to do
my own shit.

31:25.197 --> 31:27.099
You get that?
You understand that?

31:27.216 --> 31:29.806
Besides, I thought you were
gonna change your mind

31:29.831 --> 31:32.465
once you realized
I wasn't bailing.

31:34.335 --> 31:36.029
[ Clears throat ]

31:36.176 --> 31:37.621
Where were you last night,
man?

31:37.695 --> 31:40.279
I texted you, like, 10 times.

31:41.443 --> 31:42.935
Uh...

31:43.163 --> 31:45.265
Got shitfaced.

31:45.564 --> 31:47.564
Wrecked my bike.

31:47.933 --> 31:49.882
Woke up in jail.

31:52.121 --> 31:53.312
Did smurf bail you out?

31:53.421 --> 31:56.593
No. Called Nicky.

31:57.730 --> 31:59.195
What is she?
Like, your new mom?

31:59.283 --> 32:01.507
[ Chuckles ] No, but she
acted like it. Mm-hmm.

32:04.383 --> 32:05.773
I got it.

32:05.868 --> 32:07.901
You got what?
The job.

32:07.965 --> 32:09.703
As a caterer.

32:10.338 --> 32:11.837
You're gonna be a caterer?

32:11.947 --> 32:13.898
Our way in, man.

32:14.566 --> 32:17.100
For the yacht heist we
were talking about. Oh.

32:19.269 --> 32:21.414
Are you shitting me?
Used an alias,

32:21.539 --> 32:22.640
one of the ones we bought

32:22.665 --> 32:24.431
for the Indian casino thing
last year.

32:25.124 --> 32:28.070
You're lookin' at
Eric Miller,

32:28.218 --> 32:31.786
who starts his first shift
on Saturday.

32:33.394 --> 32:34.578
Mm-hmm. Well done.

32:34.645 --> 32:36.921
Huh?
Mm-hmm.

32:37.961 --> 32:39.867
You wanna have a drink?
Kick it a little bit?

32:39.932 --> 32:42.265
Hell, yeah, I do, man.
All right.

32:47.074 --> 32:50.545
[ Deadbolt unlocking ]

32:52.615 --> 32:54.481
[ Door unlocks ]

32:58.853 --> 33:02.645
♪♪

33:02.787 --> 33:04.587
[ knife clicks ]

33:16.531 --> 33:17.965
[ Thud ]

33:20.141 --> 33:21.958
[ Slices cord ]

33:22.210 --> 33:24.262
[ Mouths words ]

33:25.019 --> 33:26.753
[ Knife clicks ]

33:32.265 --> 33:33.632
[ Door opens ]

33:33.681 --> 33:35.480
[ Cords clatter ]

33:40.161 --> 33:43.263
♪♪

33:47.933 --> 33:49.880
Longer we sit here,

33:50.214 --> 33:52.434
dumber we are.

33:53.066 --> 33:55.208
She's treating you
like a punk.

34:05.753 --> 34:08.888
♪♪

34:12.012 --> 34:14.411
(Javi:) She's gonna give us
that money.

34:14.543 --> 34:16.009
[ Van door slides closed ]

34:18.498 --> 34:21.167
[ Engine starts ]

34:26.060 --> 34:28.777
All weak acids are insoluble...
True or false?

34:28.958 --> 34:30.725
How will I ever use that?

34:30.821 --> 34:32.192
Do you wanna fail
on chem again?

34:32.224 --> 34:35.911
Okay, one day, I'm gonna be,
like, driving or shopping

34:35.996 --> 34:37.606
when suddenly,
I'm gonna need to know

34:37.637 --> 34:39.302
if vinegar can release
hydrogen?

34:39.327 --> 34:41.068
Is that what you're gonna
write on your test?

34:41.092 --> 34:42.652
[ Laughs ]

34:43.371 --> 34:45.208
Okay.

34:45.757 --> 34:47.190
False.

34:47.326 --> 34:48.598
Good.
[ Chuckles ]

34:48.684 --> 34:49.902
See?

34:49.928 --> 34:51.161
[ Groans ]

34:51.313 --> 34:53.380
Oh. God, that must kill.

34:53.659 --> 34:55.793
Are you sure you don't want
some of Craig's oxy?

34:55.895 --> 34:57.591
No, I'm good.

34:58.225 --> 35:01.052
Okay, if two bodies are
the same temperature

35:01.153 --> 35:02.497
but have a different
heat capacity...

35:02.521 --> 35:04.722
It was that church on the news,
right?

35:05.309 --> 35:07.809
That's what you guys robbed?

35:08.284 --> 35:10.317
Oh, my God. I knew it!

35:10.407 --> 35:13.442
I knew it! Did heat
transfer occur or not?

35:15.190 --> 35:16.575
Oh, my God.

35:16.743 --> 35:18.286
Did you carry a gun?

35:18.380 --> 35:20.083
Holy shit. Was it a rush?

35:20.449 --> 35:22.449
How much
did you get away with?

35:23.044 --> 35:24.583
50 Grand?

35:25.254 --> 35:26.786
100?

35:28.169 --> 35:29.512
More?

35:31.270 --> 35:33.677
I'm not gonna talk about it.

35:40.916 --> 35:44.137
That's why you broke up
with me, right?

35:44.930 --> 35:47.591
To protect me from it all?

35:48.887 --> 35:51.114
So I wouldn't get sucked in?

35:54.503 --> 35:57.371
But if I wanna
get sucked in, J?

35:59.317 --> 36:02.118
What if that's what I want?

36:10.900 --> 36:14.309
♪♪

36:22.510 --> 36:25.045
[ loud crash ]

36:25.874 --> 36:28.542
- [ Whispers ] Oh, shit.
- What's going on?

36:28.850 --> 36:30.169
- Turn out that light.
- Why?

36:30.285 --> 36:31.575
Turn it out.

36:31.713 --> 36:33.179
[ Switch clicks ]

36:36.691 --> 36:37.831
- Get in the closet.
- Why?

36:37.910 --> 36:39.870
Just get in there.
Where's your phone?

